{
  "texts": [
    "This was in the sense that a structured approach helps the students navigate effectively through learning tasks, therefore providing direction.",
    "The postexperiment data collection consisted of an online questionnaire via Qualtrics, containing closed-and open-ended questions.",
    "The quantitative analysis aimed to glean insights into participants' engagement, perceptions of generative AI and personalized learning (PL), and their overall educational experiences.",
    "When asked to describe the impact of the tutor bot on their understanding of educational reform, all respondents reported that the bot was helpful.",
    "Specifically, 8% rated it as extremely helpful, 57% as very helpful, 27% as moderately helpful, and 8% as slightly helpful."
  ]
}